--  For example: Integer'Image(Color'Pos(Blue)).
--
--  Appropriate Defining_Name_Kinds:
--       A_Defining_Character_Literal
--       A_Defining_Enumeration_Literal
--
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
--  15.4 function Representation_Value_Image
